,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a93b3d2c76afd6b4b5beceaff4df37ea007da1","tid":2348100,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"因為金老世界有內功就無所不能<br />\n九劍如果唔係比風清揚/令狐沖哩類內功深厚嘅人用根本冇作為<br />\n<br />\n折梅手接到招都要用內功化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"令狐沖就係因為 受傷 冇耐力, 先至可以用到獨孤九劍"},{"pid":"09910b9fe9b27574052cfa95f0e2983c35e21c5f","tid":2348100,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2548bc0bbb028946b896a71f040c0f2018593063","tid":2348100,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfe49f248cad4acf72c30feb3a8f7145523e7331","tid":2348100,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T20:04:08.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話天山折梅<br />\n九劍<br />\n太極拳<br />\n<br />\n三大神級套路"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T20:05:01.000Z","msg":"其他武功除非係超遠距離<br />\n<br />\neg.  六脈, 彈指神通<br />\n<br />\n否則都無可能夠呢三套打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"近你點破六脈神劍"},{"pid":"2454911324590db99d9f68bd5831d9ba1ab5816c","tid":2348100,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"不如討論下搾波龍抓手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a8accee5214df5793cf1aa1a079e64a32ab05b","tid":2348100,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2548bc0bbb028946b896a71f040c0f2018593063","tid":2348100,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfe49f248cad4acf72c30feb3a8f7145523e7331","tid":2348100,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T20:04:08.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話天山折梅<br />\n九劍<br />\n太極拳<br />\n<br />\n三大神級套路"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T20:05:01.000Z","msg":"其他武功除非係超遠距離<br />\n<br />\neg.  六脈, 彈指神通<br />\n<br />\n否則都無可能夠呢三套打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"鳩摩智不容他喘息，連出兩指，嗤嗤有聲，卻是「多羅指法」。虛竹坐馬拉弓，還擊一拳，已是「 羅漢拳」中的一招「黑虎偷心」。這一招拳法粗淺之極，但附以小無相功後，竟將兩下穿金破石的多羅指指力消於中途。"},{"pi