"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"先唔講中唔中心<br />\n手都俾人斬埋都叫破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"明明天外飛仙張無忌回劍檔路先斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經放棄左劍招用倚天劍硬爆 咁叫破<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通又話東方不敗破九劍咩"},{"pid":"bae4c7beee4864de29e20b8b24c78c249e33599a","tid":2348100,"uid":278467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a67983b06a85c854e8395b1e33c71a97ffc16eae","tid":2348100,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caa82472231bbc550fb06c5d9ffc484d09ec21da","tid":2348100,"uid":278467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edfb2c24be87d4824a860c2592d55918c8c6188a","tid":2348100,"uid":71657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"楊過sad mode嘅暗然銷魂掌 先係世一武功"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:37:45.000Z","msg":"俠客行 六脈神劍 了解一下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"講緊計唔計武器先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"六脈都唔係武器"},{"pid":"f4f2200fa4060bd7c45402b4e4ee4429f23df3ff","tid":2348100,"uid":176687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e620e70b4e9da5a25cedb113d2b28f5234fa382","tid":2348100,"uid":240499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edfb2c24be87d4824a860c2592d55918c8c6188a","tid":2348100,"uid":71657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"楊過sad mode嘅暗然銷魂掌 先係世一武功"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"引佢笑就破咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"你係姑姑？"},{"pid":"d57e8dec3a6855cd485dff874b2d695798aabf47","tid":2348100,"uid":18243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51ea1bdcd767d8ee0ea9863b8d497dfd7dd27037","tid":2348100,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"這「天山折梅手」雖然只有六路，但包含了逍遙派武學的精義，掌法和擒拿手之中，含蘊有劍法、刀法、鞭法、槍法、抓法、斧法等等諸般兵刃的絕招，變法繁複，虛竹一時也學不了那許多。童姥道：「我這『天山折梅手』是永遠學不全的，將來你內功越高，見識越多，天下任何招數武功，都能自行化在這『六路折梅手』之中。好在你已學會了口訣，以後學到什麼程度，全憑你自己了。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然有話繁複但相比九劍似乎簡單太多，唔食悟性，純食內功，重劍劍法算唔算走呢一路，折梅手，重劍算唔算一種無招？<br />\n<br />\nP.S 唔洗貼九劍潮文啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a90a89a5857ca6d074456feb90b2e2251c6b43","tid":2348100,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"折梅手寫得唔多 太少資料<br />\n一認真討論就變腦補大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49587ee521f583c63b5a64936dcbd41eb5e0bcb2","tid":2348100,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b8c04ce164e026970615923fef28246eb69fc3","tid":2348100,"uid":371849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"金庸online最強一階武學...（死老鬼）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"咁多派唔放<br />\n都放靈鷲宮入去 <br />\n<br />\n折梅手算係有啲市場地位嘅"},{"pid":"0a54256e2ac9db5d7033ff967e848a0d4b5a6ffb","tid":2348100,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a90a89a5857ca6d074456feb90b2e2251c6b43","tid":2348100,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"折梅手寫得唔多 太少資料<br />\n一認真討論就變腦補大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實太極劍都唔係好多"},{"pid":"5a246f1bb7b54cc2443777bbe58aa151b4dcc1ba","tid":2348100,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"天生摺霉手<br />\n個名柒吓柒吓咁睇 見唔想練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b35ddf529f1144ada4e812c969a76bb51f4118","tid":2348100,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a246f1bb7b54cc2443777bbe58aa151b4dcc1ba","tid":2348100,"uid":286155,"like":0,"disli